FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782807585
OL,3,CResident doctors vote to end strikes
OL,4,Cafter accepting government pay offer
OL,6,FThe new package includes standard 2016
OL,7,Fresident doctor contract terms for all
OL,8,Flocally employed medics, and will mean
OL,9,Fresident doctor pay will be 35.2%
OL,10,Fhigher on average than it was four
OL,11,Fyears ago, the Department of Health
OL,12,Fand Social Care has said.
OL,14,FThere will also be 4,500 extra
OL,15,Fspecialty training places over three
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782807585
OL,3,CResident doctors vote to end strikes
OL,4,Cafter accepting government pay offer
OL,6,FDr Fletcher, however, also warned that
OL,7,F"this is by no means the end of the
OL,8,Froad for pay restoration", saying that
OL,9,Fdespite progress in the last few
OL,10,Fyears, they are "still nearly a fifth
OL,11,Fbehind 2008 levels of pay".
OL,13,F"We are putting the pay review process
OL,14,Fon notice ` if it cannot deliver
OL,15,Fcontinued pay improvements, then we
OL,16,Frisk once again falling back into
OL,17,Fdispute in future. And without genuine
OL,18,Fdelivery on the jobs front, we will
OL,19,Fonce again see training bottlenecks
OL,20,Fthrottling our careers and with it,
OL,21,Ffurther discord.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
