FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782807585
OL,3,CResident doctors vote to end strikes
OL,4,Cafter accepting government pay offer
OL,6,F"I'd like to thank everyone who stood
OL,7,Fon a picket line, who organised,
OL,8,Fargued and raised their voice on the
OL,9,Fissues of pay and jobs. Your continued
OL,10,Fdedication and refusal to give in has
OL,11,Fmoved us miles from where we started,
OL,12,Fand you should be proud. When we
OL,13,Forganise, we win."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
